{"tid":1848513,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"肺炎傳說（改編：餓狼傳說）","createTime":"2020-01-28T13:25:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T13:45:56.000Z","uid":346932,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1088f0ae8550a2322bcab74044198d62592e7658","tid":1848513,"uid":346932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:25:10.000Z","msg":"【肺炎傳說】<br />\n原曲：餓狼傳說（張學友）<br />\n改詞：勁量AAD<br />\n<br />\n高官係咁咳 司長跟肇始<br />\n痴鬼線署長 死撐未蒙面<br />\n悲醫護要抽 dirty生死籤<br />\n炒口罩酒精 假貨要明辨<br />\n<br />\n駛乜申報 怕群眾聚集倍增感染<br />\n班友虛報 有病如何被檢<br />\n<br />\n封鎖陸海空 出走急到癲<br />\n得返八個鐘 拋棄兩孩兒<br />\n高燒仲去玩 點解可咁cheap<br />\n急速降體溫 係網路炫耀<br />\n<br />\n講出真相 你話我編織亂咁造謠<br />\n終於宣佈 旅運要全停止<br />\n<br />\n刺猬樹熊駱駝竹鼠夠味濃<br />\n蝙蝠小野鹿野豬孔雀燴蛇肉<br />\n蚱蜢鱷魚白鵝蜂蛹與活蟲<br />\n海鮮街市吃野味補血又排毒<br />\n<br />\n幾千例確診 冰山一角尖<br />\n走出到他鄉 幾百萬人士<br />\n醫院大爆煲 家中等變屍<br />\n不需要檢測 火化要全面<br />\n<br />\n賓賓宣布 國內客遣返使乜畀面<br />\n金仔鎖國 廢時連累朝鮮<br />\n<br />\n武漢傳來肺炎聲稱冇蔓延<br />\n專家都中招你睇廣發就唔掂<br />\n看看国民極無知真惹人憐<br />\n駛乜口罩信政府身狀又強健<br />\n<br />\n勸你月娥及時封關抗肺炎<br />\n封得一半關妄想可隔絕攔截<br />\n去到未來疫情本土大蔓延<br />\n呢一班狗官搞衰香港到何年<br />\n<br />\n（小弟初次嘗試 請大家多多指教 畀下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"51f3a4ccbde85a0952070587643f8581f8678351","tid":1848513,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88fefce9a65179478f00968d2e5684da6f938b29","tid":1848513,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:45:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請廣傳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請幫手入去比正評</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手足裝備抗沙士：防毒面具/濾罐 (型號/分析/用法/清潔全齊）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848447</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整體分析圖：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F116690396531818%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=dcf67287\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n</a><br />\n個別仔細分析：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">護目鏡</span>：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845419</a></span></span> / <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F117867026414155&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=3f11a3f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/?d=n<br />\n<br />\nVPN 大踢爆：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D112386483628876%26id%3D112357283631796%26__tn__%3D%252As-R&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=1e89698a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家廣傳，避免沉底<br />\n<br />\n最近口罩同N95 都賣曬，部分手足屋企口罩已經就黎用盡，今日同大家介紹下可以防沙士+TG嘅濾罐同濾棉。第一，係for 用曬/買唔到口罩嘅手足，第二係希望方便大家一次過買齊發夢+出街嘅裝備，就算沙士完左，自用送禮都可以繼續名貴大方。<br />\n<br />\nN95/R95/P95 口罩基本上係particulate respirator, 外科口罩防嘅係飛沫粒子，即係我地用防毒面具代替，就要裝particulate filter，換言之，就係濾棉！<br />\n<br />\n濾棉最高級別就係P100，防油性+非油性粒子，即係TG（油性）同埋病毒都可以防，型號包括2091, 2097, 2297, 6035（只有英國製）,7093 等等，而60926等等嘅6092X 系列濾罐，因為內置P100 濾棉，所以一樣ok <br />\n其中，6053 同 7093 棉係防水的，清潔消毒會較方便，而60926表面亦有膠盒。<br />\n<br />\n有強國人做過測試，係北京霧霾毒氣之下，3M 2091 用左十一日過濾能力都係跌左1%，手足請自行考慮幾耐換一次。<br />\n<br />\nAmazon 大log買亦有便，大家可以組團買。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3m.com.au/3M/en_AU/company-au/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3/?N=5002385+8711017+3294471754&amp;rt=rud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.com.au%2F3M%2Fen_AU%2Fcompany-au%2Fall-3m-products%2F~%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3%2F%3FN%3D5002385%2B8711017%2B3294471754%26rt%3Drud&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=4312af69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.com.au/3M/en_AU/company-au/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3/?N=5002385+8711017+3294471754&amp;rt=rud</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3m.com/3M/en_US/company-us/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case/?N=5002385+3294776429&amp;rt=rud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.com%2F3M%2Fen_US%2Fcompany-us%2Fall-3m-products%2F~%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case%2F%3FN%3D5002385%2B3294776429%26rt%3Drud&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=5c2537e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.com/3M/en_US/company-us/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case/?N=5002385+3294776429&amp;rt=rud</a><br />\n<br />\n2003 年沙士，淘大嘅清理人員就係用2091棉+600X 罐（罐理論上唔洗，應該係防佢地嘅清潔同消毒藥水）。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">如何清潔防毒面具可參考依段片，有教disinfection，主要都係漂白水同消毒劑<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdE5IweYn3T4&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=def8912f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n清潔步驟：<br />\n入到屋企唔好除裝備住，用酒精紙巾抹左面具同濾棉/罐表面先，跟住抹埋手再洗手（點解又要酒精又要洗手係有原因的），跟住就除面罩，再跟番片入面嘅教學清潔<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n防毒面具方面，建議大家買/用6800 或者其他包曬成塊面嘅款式，咁樣就唔洗帶眼罩，一舊野保護曬成塊面，最安全。因為你戴半面+眼罩，咁就多舊野清潔，同埋部分眼罩封唔曬，冇咁安全。<br />\n<br />\n型號方面，全面嘅建議大家買6800，順便擋埋橡膠子彈，半面嘅就買7502/ 6500，兩款手足都表示舒適度幾高。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112044766987392%2Fposts%2F119490526242816%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=9b606b8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n</a><br />\n酒精搓手液 vs 洗手梘液</span>"}]}